    <title>Crystalizer</title>
    <p>
        This plugin can be used to add a little of dynamic range to songs that were
        overly compressed
    </p>
    <terms>
        <item>
            <title>
                <em style="strong" its:withinText="nested">Aggressive Mode</em>
            </title>
            <p>
                When this option is enabled sample amplitude dependent amplification will be
                applied to the signal. Take care to not saturate the next plugin in the
                processing chain.
            </p>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>
                <em style="strong" its:withinText="nested">Intensities</em>
            </title>
            <p>
                The higher the value the higher is the difference in magnitude between the
                loudest and the quietest sounds. You can set different intensities for each
                frequency band.
            </p>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>
                <em style="strong" its:withinText="nested">Bypass</em>
            </title>
            <p>
                When active the audio signal passing through this band will not be modified.
            </p>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>
                <em style="strong" its:withinText="nested">Mute</em>
            </title>
            <p>
                Silence the band.
            </p>
        </item>
    </terms>
